00:42:38.286 --> 00:42:39.280
who the buyer is.
 

00:42:39.280 --> 00:42:43.498
We have this one buyer here,
and I'm just looking at it in a

00:42:43.498 --> 00:42:46.206
four-year period,
bought five houses,

00:42:46.206 --> 00:42:48.829
six houses, all with the same
broker,

00:42:48.829 --> 00:42:51.079
