00:42:58.449 --> 00:43:03.753
So, I would put the question
back here, who's the lion and

00:43:03.753 --> 00:43:06.639
who's the zebra in this case?
 

00:43:06.639 --> 00:43:08.539
Was it the iBanks?
 

00:43:08.539 --> 00:43:12.804
They were relying on these
folks in Cleveland to do a

00:43:12.804 --> 00:43:19.083
